&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Vacancies for 111 Clinical Advisors&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hours:&lt;/strong&gt;Flexible working including days, evenings, weekends&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Contract Type: &lt;/strong&gt;Permanent&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Salary: &lt;/strong&gt;From £15.09 per hour&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt;Vocare House Newcastle&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are recruiting for NHS111 Clinical Advisors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you a Registered Nurse or Paramedic?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Do you want to make a difference in someone’s life?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a role with less physical demands with flexibility around your working hours?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vocare work in partnership with the NHS across the region to provide accessible and high-quality integrated health care services. The Integrated Urgent Care Clinical Assessment Service operates 24/7, 365 days a year. It provides access to telephone triage, face to face consultation as well as digital online access points for patients and health care professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Facts:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Founded in 1996&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;9.2 million patients across the UK&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2,000 employees&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What’sit like to work here?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&quot;Our service has a friendly, welcoming atmosphere and is the most inclusive environment where we all respect each other as individuals and colleagues which enables us to provide a superb, seamless care for callers to our telephone triage service&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Where do you fit in?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anywhere and everywhere, whatever your dream career or experience, Vocare is looking for the passion and drive to bring the company to the next level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the job:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to growth we have opportunities for Clinicians where you will be supporting Health Advisors by delivering patient care using your clinical knowledge as well as our bespoke triage system. You will be required to assess patient&#39;s symptoms, giving advice and referring when necessary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We require you to complete our unique Pathways Training programme which will last for roughly 6 weeks, you will receive full pay and a pathways licence. We offer a part-time or a full-time course for your training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In addition to a competitive salary Vocare also offer the following benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;30 days pro rata holiday entitlement (including bank holidays)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company Pension Scheme or NHS Pension – where applicable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perk box and access to NHS staff benefit schemes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Employee Assistance Programme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company sick pay after one year of service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company Maternity/Paternity pay after one year of service&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to updates and courses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Free onsite parking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Registered Nurse, Paramedic or Pharmacist with current NMC or HCPC Registration&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;General or child nursing qualifications&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Significant relevant experience Which would include primary or emergency care&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Closing date for ALL applications is 28th October 2020&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please note the following shortlisting approach will be applied:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Round 1&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;- Any staff at risk of redundancy within the Totally plc group, who meet the essential criteria, will be considered in the first instance for this vacancy.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Round 2&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;- If the vacancy has not been filled after round 1, any employee Affected by Change within the Totally plc group, who meet the essential criteria, will be then be considered for this vacancy.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Round 3&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;- If the vacancy has not been filled after round 2, we will consider and shortlist all remaining applications in accordance with our recruitment policy.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please assume you have been unsuccessful with your application if you have not heard back from us within 2 weeks of the closing date.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;All successful applicants will be subject to a DBS Check&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
